’Ů@bedd709691b49a6c8f9c2180455cf64c10902783fabdbff14eea30b51da10881ŮĂTitle: title: to toml
Path: Examples
Content:
Outputs an TOML string representing the contents of this record.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> {foo: 1 bar: 'qwe'} | to toml
foo = 1
bar = "qwe"


```
